{"tid":2501433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔太欣賞籃球呢項運動","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:09:33.000Z","uid":396317,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2484115ff4d706b2432b4047d84e8b9c385098fa","tid":2501433,"uid":396317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"1. 冷氣波<br />\n2. 打打下成日停停停<br />\n3. 睇最後一節就可以，前面全部垃圾時間<br />\n4. 十條友屈高屈大隻<br />\n5. 冇降班，打完成季，最渣嗰啲仲有咩選秀權<br />\n6. 根本上就係十個麻甩佬玩玩具，撞離撞去<br />\n7. 因為個籃比較細，入波嘅款都係差唔多<br />\n8. 啲計時三分賽，極度沒有意思，同自己一個對住牆猜乒乓波鬥猜得多下大同小異<br />\n9. 籃球除咗NBA冇人會睇<br />\n10. 暫停機制極度弱智，對比踢波去角球旗拖延時間，踢波個波係仲係個場入面，個比賽仲進行緊<br />\n<br />\n總結：打籃球=玩玩具，冇刺激性<br />\n<br />\n最弱智係入完球三分對住鏡頭懶型慶祝，成場百幾分，有咩咁威？"},{"pid":"9051fd7c852b269d3f593ed42148f8907cb30a49","tid":2501433,"uid":345877,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"你真係唔識㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445214996c1d6565d4916f50b6a4cc64a7d9bfc9","tid":2501433,"uid":342128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d6fe8380e70698d0aa958a1f8b72bc1c8c6a23","tid":2501433,"uid":143380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"好似動物園咁睇住啲大猩猩將個波放落個網到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e75fc8c7631ad31ae5e4966f8375a0626683487","tid":2501433,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5106dff388d500f5cacd8f3f550fe10ce7166474","tid":2501433,"uid":135141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re